{"tid":2425426,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鬧翻20年最後談周星馳　深信再搭檔「一定有機會」卻留憾　","createTime":"2021-02-27T10:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T10:41:00.000Z","uid":116696,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"38e1b84fd3ac1e8030cdf6faa5317df5352de11f","tid":2425426,"uid":116696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:38:35.000Z","msg":"70歲港星吳孟達曾是周星馳（星爺）電影的「最佳綠葉」，2人在銀幕上默契極佳的喜劇表演堪稱經典，不過，這對最佳拍檔，卻從2001年《少林足球》後至今20年再無合作，影壇屢傳雙方有心結，吳孟達早年受訪，被問與星爺的友情消失是否遺憾？他不避諱直言有時也在想2人情誼變淡的原因，感嘆說：「現在感覺有一點&hellip;&hellip;老死不相往來那種感覺。」吳孟達最後一次公開亮相是在中國綜藝《王牌對王牌》22日播出的訪問，最後有人問他和周星馳（星爺）有可能再搭檔嗎？他一句：「我還沒死，他還沒退休，一定有機會的。」如今吳孟達走了，再沒機會搭檔，令人唏噓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210227/LN5VSSQ3TFCWNKFYIR3XVF5V2U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210227%2FLN5VSSQ3TFCWNKFYIR3XVF5V2U%2F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=118fe535\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210227%2FLN5VSSQ3TFCWNKFYIR3XVF5V2U%2F&h=68af1cd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210227/LN5VSSQ3TFCWNKFYIR3XVF5V2U/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對上一次合作已經係20年前少林足球<br />\n達叔都講到出口想同周星馳拍檔返<br />\n周星馳好狠心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd32530376af02596417b91e5eb1709c7adf081a","tid":2425426,"uid":69083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"R.I.P.<br />\n祝達叔 來世再做中蟈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}